{"tid":473572,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"二戰嘅日本喺太平洋拖咗美軍咁耐, 算唔算超額完成任務?","createTime":"2017-11-19T11:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T11:00:20.000Z","uid":143499,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"da479cf0d3ff70f1a911fcf7d2367849bda6c9bc","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:15:07.000Z","msg":"太平洋戰爭打咗近四年， 日本一個頂曬美國同埋commonwealth， 論人口論資源都一定唔夠美國加英國加澳洲，Mid-way 四格正規航母收曬皮都可以撐到原爆。<br />\n以寡敵眾嚟講算唔算好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00289cece1403962469e044432070e040e3b233","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"利申唔係崇日撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59802f4c8d1e71495dd62c54b6ed9188678c5eb6","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:50:27.000Z","msg":"認真學術討論，pish"},{"pid":"30228fd26ac57d294e691f47c57fc9d72790a0db","tid":473572,"uid":53122,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"美國佬掛住打德國佬<br />\n唔得閒理班㗎仔hea應住先"},{"pid":"4fbed00a531108c5f8785596f5e772a994f2ad87","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國佬掛住打德國佬<br />\n唔得閒理班㗎仔hea應住先</blockquote><br />\n但係我記得美國好似冇點樣同德國打個海戰, 大西洋都冇CV,好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c99399148edcf8ae6b21b7b0ff7f2c28024ff81","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:39:44.000Z","msg":"btw 點解學術post會得正皮,冇人留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9541d4648dfeb9b30febb042ca7b4af17edd8b","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"keep pishing"},{"pid":"370d31db4532f7719ab3d398f4b83bc9b774d5c8","tid":473572,"uid":142965,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"你個標題講到好似英美係入侵者 日本先係防禦方咁款"},{"pid":"6df54b357bd2b97460e4343c4cb4f4d0560c4882","tid":473572,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d2520aee42843a78abaeaf22a37bae9a686d539","tid":473572,"uid":92178,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48aaa59581004ebd10810f26248c375e333c65bb","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個標題講到好似英美係入侵者 日本先係防禦方咁款</blockquote><br />\n我冇講錯喎<br />\n根據山本五十六嘅講法日本襲擊珍珠港係想快啲同美國議和， 係日本撩佢打先， 但係日本一早預咗唔夠打， 諗住拖得就拖。<br />\n所以我嘅意思唔係話英美先係侵略者， 而係日本用咁缺乏嘅資源底下可以撳住英國同澳洲你打， 拖延美國咁耐。<br />\n坦白講美國對付日本嘅比重唔會少過德國好多， 即使歐洲失守仲有個海可以隔著美洲同歐洲; 但係中途島同埋珍珠港一失手就會直， 畀日本有機會喺機場直接炸夏威夷同埋關島甚至美國本土。"},{"pid":"8ecf8da0b320ba54a4634f9acb66a65ec6e6e7bb","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"老老竇竇， 次次打親仗尤其係空戰紅海戰美國係人數都幾打一，但係前期至中期幾乎好多都係慘勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲士兵寧願去打德國人都唔夠膽打日本仔， 搞到好多士兵有精神病唔只係戰爭 嗰啲後遺症， 台真係痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845117943b8ab57c9669e3d5f97eea1cfc19ed82","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會係美國輕敵所以先會搞到咁麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563ec30c0e348d76d50bb0c220aa6f29927eda9f","tid":473572,"uid":130365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"日本係傾盡全部船/航母 去打太平洋喎, 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國果陣打midway 用3架航母 收左日本4架航母皮 , 美國先損毀左一架<br />\n講實力midway 見真章, 仲都未計佢後期工業開埋金手指起航母 <br />\n日本後期技窮就拎部大和號出去自殺扮光榮犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b4e43ee5826ec77702661138bd4ec01a9175dc","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本係傾盡全部船/航母 去打太平洋喎, 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國果陣打midway 用3架航母 收左日本4架航母皮 , 美國先損毀左一架<br />\n講實力midway 見真章, 仲都未計佢後期工業開埋金手指起航母 <br />\n日本後期技窮就拎部大和號出去自殺扮光榮犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果唔係南雲忠一自把自為下令啲飛機裝炸彈而唔係魚雷, 咁喺日本發現美國嗰陣美國嗰三架航母一定玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為南雲忠一諗住裝炸彈炸機場冇諗過會遇到美國艦隊， 最尾成隊飛機都係裝曬炸彈，無魚雷， 所以即使日本發現美國先報失去咗突襲嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再加上日本本身個技術唔係好差, 喺飛機方面後期嘅N1K2, A7M, J2M 都好勁不過冇資源量產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有一樣嘢日本真係完全超越美國， 酸素魚雷嘅射程同埋隱藏性都極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以USN啲戰艦經常迴避唔到日本啲魚雷"},{"pid":"e275be90d833975ba55f1e9d1b44e103447c5954","tid":473572,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"不過你講起大和號， 都係一個悲劇。<br />\n因為嗰陣嘅日本<del>地球聯邦</del>仲係堅持大艦巨砲主義所以比美國<del>自護公國</del>嗰啲飛機同埋航母<del>MS</del>收咗皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0da54169c765e73efe4895e2259a008aab4730","tid":473572,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國佬掛住打德國佬<br />\n唔得閒理班㗎仔hea應住先</blockquote><br />\n但係我記得美國好似冇點樣同德國打個海戰, 大西洋都冇CV,好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class